<br>
I have a question that has been raising differnt anwsers from selected people I have asked. This has to do with Alt Exp arch abilities.<br>
<br>
I play a 60th level Enchanter with now 18 points <br>
General<br>
(3) running <br>
(3) metabolism<br>
<br>
Arch<br>
3/3 Channelling Focus (15% modification to channelling)<br>
<br>
I also wear a 3% mod to channelling boots bringing the total to 18% Channel Mod.<br>
<br>
Now the enchanters are capped at 220 Channelling @ 60th level.<br>
<br>
