<br>
the 18% is just a modifier of the &quot;chance&quot; of success for that specific spell casting ability - hense for channelling I am getting beat on and have an 18% better chance to complete &quot;regain concentration&quot; and complete my cast?<br>
<br>
Thanks for the time<br>
<br>
Alumar<br>
